title: Hour 3 - Cooper Rush or Dak Prescott, Can Anybody Stop Daniel Snyder?
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Cooper Rush or Dak Prescott, Can Anybody Stop Daniel Snyder?
description:
Dan wonders if the Dallas Cowboys are still trying to rush Dak Prescot back from injury. And he also wonders if NFL Commissioner Roger Goodell has any recourse when dealing with defiant Washington Commanders Owner, Daniel Snyder.
